    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hey! We actually already have a list of DOM that should be outputted by InstantSearch in a separate project, but since that's a major change, we will do that all at once. \r\n\r\nFor now, what problem do you have with the css with it being there? As a workaround you should be able to make it \"completely gone\" with display: contents like this:\r\n\r\n```css\r\n.ais-current-refined-values--body div {\r\n  display: contents;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nOr you can do the changes you planned to do on the body on the div instead. \r\n\r\nI hope that helps!",
