    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Wow, I wasn't aware of `display: contents` yet, that's nice, thanks! Still, it's a patch of course, and needs a polyfill, and I just like clean html😭, but this should work.\r\n\r\n[I've made a tiny proposal](https://github.com/jasperkennis/instantsearch.js/tree/move-body-class-on-current-refined-values) for moving the class one layer deeper but I suppose that too counts as a patch, and would be a major change to incorporate anyway.\r\n\r\nOut of curiosity, can I see that list you're referring to?",
