    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "That patch looks good, and would indeed be the way to go. The list isn’t public, but if you send me an email (haroen@algolia.com), I can give you access to see it, since you’re interested. \r\n\r\nI’ll close this issue now, since it’s not _too_ big of a problem, and you have your patch as a change, as well as the issue will be resolved when we do this widget rewrite. \r\n\r\nFeel free to comment further though. ",
